Q. Use case : Write a Secure Architecture design for an AI Document Processing Platform common in companies building AI-powered SaaS products (legal document analysis, medical record summarization, contract extraction, etc.). 
Companies running such workloads often use cloud platforms like Amazon Web Services or Google Cloud and orchestrate services with Kubernetes while using service meshes such as Istio.
Secure Network & Control Plane Architecture
Covers:
	• VPC segmentation
	• Private/public subnet design
	• Egress filtering
	• Service mesh mTLS
	• Control plane vs data plane separation
	• Bastion host risk
  • Admin plane hardening

