Compromised container tries:
- privilege escalation
- lateral movement
- service impersonation

Q. Why here?
Workers process untrusted documents.
Malicious files may exploit parser libraries.

-> Mitigation:
- container isolation
- seccomp profiles
- read-only filesystem
- runtime security monitoring

